'''Snillik''' was a thick [[Liqueur/Legends|liqueur]] produced somewhere in the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] absolutely hated it, so he often chose it to drink while [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]], sipping it slowly. This allowed him to "drink socially," while staying sober and keeping his senses keen.

